#\\\|CZ3YLTVEYQ2YSWMGBWASFE5QA76TKFLVKPWVEK5QUY3Q77LW2HG \ / AMOS7 \ YOURUM ::
#\[7]EC7WGF5YAAA2UPTFGHWQK577RKGLLFNV3XOXE4AJBTNBLUYWDACI 7  DATA SIGNATURE ::
#:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
